description: **Bondi Rescue Roleplay** is a roleplay group based of the real life show, **Bondi Rescue**. We have over 17k members and we're fast-growing too! At Bondi Rescue Roleplay, you can enjoy the nice relaxing beach that we have on offer, you can become a Junior Lifeguard and help save those who need saving; don't worry there's a-lot more jobs on offer too! In our Communications Server you can communicate with other Bondi group members, make friends and be the first to know about any upcoming update and/or features.
